{"tid":8862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[一丘] 不滿刪facebook上追糧影片 3名uber司機毆admin報仇","createTime":"2016-11-28T12:55:57.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T15:11:02.000Z","uid":17103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc881eae53ff97281a1a6d2b46809aedaf7bbedb","tid":8862,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:55:57.000Z","msg":"2016-11-28 17:23:00 HKT<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20161128/280pix/1480324982_b256.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161128%2F280pix%2F1480324982_b256.jpg&h=1cbf8780&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告何斌權<br />\n負責管理社交網站facebook「uber」群組的uber司機，早前刪去司機到uber辦公室「追糧」的影片，惹來部份司機不滿。8月22日他凌晨將車停在大埔充電站時被3名遭欠薪的uber司機拳打腳踢5分鐘，面頰、前額、頸部及雙手受傷。警方事後拘捕該三名行兇司機，他們今在粉嶺法院承認傷人罪，遭還柙候判。<br />\n<br />\n被告何斌權（42歲）、張順恒（37歲）、及吳兆堅（30歲），承認案發日在大埔科技大道東Tesla充電站非法及惡意傷害林俊偉（42歲）。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情時指，三人分別被uber欠薪3萬、2萬及2.4萬元，他們與事主原不相識，但從網絡知悉事主鼓勵不發薪給被「欠糧」的uber司機，引起三人不滿。有被告認得事主車牌，事發當晚在充電站巧遇事主，遂上前與他理論，是事主出手打吳在先，三人才動手，三人沒使用武器，望能輕判。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官指三人雖沒有使用武器，但三人圍毆一人屬加重刑罰因素，現索閱其背景報告，他們須還柙至下月19日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n其中被告何斌權因「追糧」事件襲擊uber職員，今年9月承認普通襲擊罪被判罰款2,000元。"},{"pid":"ea23a8e050a2b4a6d995c59d08cf5650056f36e8","tid":8862,"uid":39517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T08:02:07.000Z","msg":"推  外賣果邊好多人被拖糧"},{"pid":"241a4e3d671f315b87dfff54c31aeab8a0ad331d","tid":8862,"uid":38218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T08:05:30.000Z","msg":"不滿被bam, 眾巴打圍毆Admin"},{"pid":"d0e85243c2397b7e85b49fb5394876999e075805","tid":8862,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T08:10:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勇武<br />\n<br />\nBTW call4van先係最高質"},{"pid":"246e01ae15c87f356141e8ddafe04517b2d1c9e1","tid":8862,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:27:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推  外賣果邊好多人被拖糧</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你講真架 .. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實做外賣真係唔知點賺.<br />\n除非你講有人比幾十你健下身. . ."},{"pid":"f890e531495169783aa7da834cbc7aa91c335472","tid":8862,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:28:03.000Z","msg":"聽朋友講，Uber真係有拖糧情況"},{"pid":"75802610b1b9e258b602c9184f432e3eef1283b6","tid":8862,"uid":28438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:37:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勇武<br />\n<br />\nBTW call4van先係最高質</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAgger"},{"pid":"3e13c8b5b7902dc4608d2c2f3d5a4715ac8b412b","tid":8862,"uid":26985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:41:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽朋友講，Uber真係有拖糧情況</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上次坐uber，撩個司機吹水<br />\n個司機係咁屌uber<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8abc4443f96986577c2b353729f21c59e16840e3","tid":8862,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T15:11:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}